#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/ma/extras.py:docstring
#: of numpy.ma.extras.masked_all_like:36
msgid ""
"Unlike other masked array creation functions (e.g. `numpy.ma.zeros_like`, "
"`numpy.ma.ones_like`, `numpy.ma.full_like`), `masked_all_like` does not "
"initialize the values of the array, and may therefore be marginally faster. "
"However, the values stored in the newly allocated array are arbitrary. For "
"reproducible behavior, be sure to set each element of the array before "
"reading."
msgstr ""

